<plot>Cassie has been in a constant and palpable state of grief for a long time because the loss of a loved one brought her life crashing down around her. Soon she starts to see apparitions as she relives the fateful moments that caused such emotional havoc. Her friends and family struggle to come to terms with how these new problems push her to the edge of sanity. But Cassie discovers that the ghosts she has been seeing out of the corner of her eye may be much more just memories.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?012576</url></doc>
